Your pom.xml has a few issues:

Spring Boot 4.1.0 is not a standard released version. If you intended to use Spring Boot 3.x, use 3.5.x (or the version required by your project).

You're missing the MapStruct annotation processor.

You're missing the Maven Compiler Plugin configuration.

The test dependencies should be spring-boot-starter-test instead of spring-boot-starter-data-jpa-test and spring-boot-starter-webmvc-test.

Here's a corrected pom.xml for Java 17 + Spring Boot + MapStruct + Lombok + MySQL:

